rComments: Great Prof! Favourite course I've ever taken. All the other comments get the details

This guy's awesome. He's really down to earth and with the times. Lectures are engaging and interesting. He has a good sense of humor. Offers lots of easy marks (ie.10% for attendance & participation). He's a little picky on essays, but overall marks very reasonably- you get what you deserve. I highly recommend his classes.
His lectures were clear, interesting and worth attending. He's funny and insightful and pushes you to do well. Over all, really good prof. :)
Excellent Prof! Hope to take his course again!!!  Good Jokes
